# SARD India: Marketing Website
## Complete Data Specification & UI Content Document

**Purpose:** This document outlines all data, text, and UI elements for each section of the SARD marketing website. Use this as a specification guide for AI tools or web developers.

**Note:** Each section (except Home) should be a separate page accessible from main navigation.

---

## PAGE 0: HOME PAGE (LANDING PAGE)

### Section: Hero Banner

**UI Component:** Full-screen hero section with background image/gradient

**Content Elements:**

| Element | Content | Type | Notes |
|---------|---------|------|-------|
| Main Headline | "SARD India: Your Center of Excellence" | Text | Large, bold, prominent |
| Subheadline | "Delivering world-class engineering solutions across PlayStation, Television, Camera, and emerging technologies" | Text | Supporting message |
| CTA Button 1 | "Explore Our Capabilities" | Button | Links to Technical Excellence page |
| CTA Button 2 | "Connect With Us" | Button | Links to Contact/Onboarding page |
| Background | Sony blue gradient with subtle geometric pattern | Image/Design | Professional, modern aesthetic |

**Design Notes:**
- Hero should be 100% viewport height
- Text should be centered and readable over background
- Buttons should have hover effects
- Mobile: Stack buttons vertically

---

### Section: Quick Stats Overview

**UI Component:** 4-card statistic display

**Content Elements:**

| Stat | Number | Description | Icon |
|------|--------|-------------|------|
| Total Engineers | 450+ | Skilled workforce | People/Team icon |
| Active Projects | 15+ | Ongoing initiatives | Project icon |
| Sony Verticals | 5 | Business units served | Organization icon |
| Tech Domains | 8+ | Technology expertise areas | Technology icon |

**Design Notes:**
- Cards should be in a responsive grid (4 across on desktop, 2x2 on tablet, 1 on mobile)
- Each card has background color, icon, number in large font, description
- Cards should have subtle shadow and hover animation

---

### Section: Featured Sections (Navigation Preview)

**UI Component:** 6-card grid showing main sections with preview text

**Card 1: Journey & Growth**
- Title: "Our Journey"
- Description: "From 2015 startup to center of excellence with 450+ engineers across 5 Sony verticals"
- Icon: Timeline or rocket icon
- Link: Goes to Section 1 page

**Card 2: Technical Excellence**
- Title: "Technical Excellence"
- Description: "Deep expertise across 8+ technology domains including cloud, AI, and full-stack development"
- Icon: Code or technology icon
- Link: Goes to Section 2 page

**Card 3: Domain Expertise**
- Title: "Domain Excellence"
- Description: "Proven expertise in gaming, consumer electronics, imaging, audio, semiconductors, and VR"
- Icon: Chart or expertise icon
- Link: Goes to Section 3 page

**Card 4: Device Mastery**
- Title: "Device Excellence"
- Description: "Portfolio spanning PlayStation, BRAVIA, Cameras, VR, and semiconductor solutions"
- Icon: Devices icon
- Link: Goes to Section 4 page

**Card 5: Our Team**
- Title: "Why Choose SARD"
- Description: "Certified experts, secure infrastructure, global support, proven track record"
- Icon: Award or check icon
- Link: Goes to Section 8 page

**Card 6: Success Stories**
- Title: "Case Studies"
- Description: "Real projects, measurable impact, proven capabilities across verticals"
- Icon: Trophy or success icon
- Link: Goes to Section 6 page

---

