### Section 2E: Architecture Layers & Infrastructure

**UI Component:** Vertical architecture diagram (or stacked cards)

**Layer 1: Presentation Layer (UI/UX)**
- Components: "Web frontends, Mobile apps, Desktop applications, VR/AR interfaces"
- Technologies: "React, Angular, Vue.js, React Native, Unity, Unreal Engine"
- Expertise: "Responsive design, Progressive Web Apps, accessibility"
- Team Size: "120+ UI/UX engineers and designers"

**Layer 2: API & Gateway Layer**
- Components: "REST APIs, GraphQL, gRPC, API Gateway"
- Technologies: "Express.js, FastAPI, Spring Boot, ASP.NET Core"
- Expertise: "High-performance APIs, rate limiting, versioning, security"
- Team Size: "80+ API and integration engineers"

**Layer 3: Application/Business Logic Layer**
- Components: "Microservices, Business logic engines, Workflow orchestration"
- Technologies: "Java, C#, Python, Node.js, Kubernetes"
- Expertise: "Domain-driven design, event-driven architecture, scalability"
- Team Size: "150+ backend engineers"

**Layer 4: Data Layer**
- Components: "SQL databases, NoSQL databases, Data warehouses, Data lakes"
- Technologies: "PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Redis, Elasticsearch, BigQuery"
- Expertise: "Database optimization, replication, backup, disaster recovery"
- Team Size: "60+ data engineers and DBAs"

**Layer 5: Security Layer**
- Components: "Authentication, Authorization, Encryption, Compliance"
- Technologies: "OAuth 2.0, JWT, SSL/TLS, AWS KMS, OWASP compliance"
- Expertise: "Zero-trust security, penetration testing, compliance management"
- Team Size: "40+ security engineers"

**Layer 6: Infrastructure & DevOps**
- Components: "Servers, Networking, Monitoring, CI/CD, Container orchestration"
- Technologies: "Docker, Kubernetes, Jenkins, Terraform, Prometheus, ELK Stack"
- Expertise: "Infrastructure as Code, automated deployments, zero-downtime releases"
- Team Size: "50+ DevOps and infrastructure engineers"

