## GENERAL DESIGN & UX GUIDELINES

### Color Palette
- Primary Blue: #0070D2 (Sony blue)
- Dark Blue: #003087 (Dark accent)
- Dark Text: #1A1A1A
- Light Background: #F5F5F5
- Accent: #FF6600 (for highlights)

### Typography
- Headlines: Bold, 28-48px
- Subheadings: Semi-bold, 18-24px
- Body: Regular, 14-16px
- Mono for code: Courier New

### Components
- Buttons: Filled (primary), Outlined (secondary)
- Cards: Subtle shadow, hover effect
- Forms: Clean labels, validation messages
- Icons: Consistent 24-32px size

### Responsive Breakpoints
- Mobile: 320px
- Tablet: 768px
- Desktop: 1024px+

